(1)
1555 Flatbush Ave., at the S.E. corner of Nostrand Ave., showing the
Brown House, now (1936) demolished.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, showing more of the corner.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)
The same, another angle. No.building in this view is standing in 1929. The
Brown House was demolished in 1924.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
